{"tid":1448414,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:32:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T17:37:01.000Z","uid":30236,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"94d5198078958be5b73f486fa52cd90a8609ff31","tid":1448414,"uid":30236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:32:02.000Z","msg":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大群：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=4tZOiqwfeINLG3hE5eaPvPGl%2B26pDsgLotMYn9d4AWI%3D&h=f7fb43f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n實時Channel:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=4tZOiqwfeINLG3hE5eaPvPGl%2B26pDsgLotMYn9d4AWI%3D&h=2cc0aebb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"78249797b6cf48102a8d3e13715ae5a18012a5a8","tid":1448414,"uid":163865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:32:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"175063426140e895564686d1726766aec6805224","tid":1448414,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:32:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"406c981578597d2679a77f43d91d9c27cb7ef7ce","tid":1448414,"uid":170445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:32:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"439f00f729d97b3425dc9ebba3004b127efc7d11","tid":1448414,"uid":30236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:33:38.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"00cd4dcdf9c908468699c66b3556e6cb46a82742","tid":1448414,"uid